# Separation of concerns

## App layers

Do not mix UI and logic in one file:

```
apps/<app-name>/src/
  main.ts(x)   # bootstrap only
  ui/          # DOM/components; no business logic
  logic/       # pure; no DOM
  state/       # optional
  types.ts
```

- `logic/`: framework-free pure functions (testability)
- `ui/`: import and call logic; no calculations/decisions

## Extract to `lib/<lib-name>/` when

- Used (or clearly will be) by 2+ apps, or
- Domain-agnostic utility (dates, RNG, shared UI)

Requirements: `package.json` with `name` (`@playground/<lib-name>`) + `exports`; unit tests; no app-specific types/copy.
